title: Arvind Vegda Bigg Boss 9 contestant: Bhai Bhai singer makes his hatke presence felt!
text:
Arvind Vegda Bigg Boss 9 contestant: Bhai Bhai singer makes his hatke presence felt! By India.com Entertainment Desk on October 11, 2015 at 11:31 PM Comments 
Bigg Boss 9 premier has created tremendous excitement. There are interesting contestants being introduced for the season one of them is singer Arvind Vegda. Vegda is known for his versatility and cutting edge musical experimentations. He is popular for his Bhai Bhai composition.which became a cult compositions for Garba events. Vegda is extremely passionate about music and he also helps budding musicians realse their potential and dreams. Vegda has caught our attention with his hatke look. ALSO READ: Bigg Boss 9 Premier: Have you seen Salman Khan’s new look for the gala night! 
Here’s how we rate the music enthusiast. 
His entry: His entry was noisy, shocking and loud. But for that loud entry he gets 7 on 10 
Style quotient: His quirky, loud and over-the top. But hey does stand out with his personality 7.5 on 10 
How promising does he look? Looks like he will be fun to watch but will he manipulate to win the title and above all win audiences vote for him? 7 on 10 on that count!
